<plot>On June 28th 1389 at Kosovo Polje, the army of Serbian emperor Lazar made a stand against the advancing Ottoman forces of Sultan Murat, resulting in a great battle which would later inspire Serbian folk tales and poems about courage, sacrifice, betrayal and tragedy. The movie was made for the 600th anniversary of the event.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?077985</url></doc>
